Pico 5 active firmware: color-coded button sequence.

This folder name is historical. It no longer runs the phone/window prop puzzle.
Archived phone/window code is in:

../../pico-back-room-blender-final/unused-future-puzzles/

Hardware:
- GPIO 15: first configured color button
- GPIO 16: second configured color button

Main topics:
- Publishes escape/pico5/color_sequence_complete
- Publishes escape/pico5/color_sequence_error
- Subscribes escape/cmd/pico5/enable_color_button_sequence
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/status_request
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/reset_puzzle

